descriptionNullable:
### Content

This data consists of 3.5 years currency exchange info for several currencies.

### Column Description

currency_from: source currency 
currency_to: target currency
currency_value: exchange rate
date: correspondent date.


### Inspiration

Currency information can affect especially sales trends. So, adding this data to your initial dataset may improve your model result.

### Note
This data is updated every week.
